Package org.gbif.predicate.query

Class EsQueryVisitor<S extends org.gbif.api.model.common.search.SearchParameter>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.predicate.query.EsQueryVisitor<S>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.gbif.api.query.QueryVisitor
    public class EsQueryVisitor<S extends org.gbif.api.model.common.search.SearchParameter>
extends Object
implements org.gbif.api.query.QueryVisitor
    The class translates predicates in GBIF download API to equivalent Elasticsearch query requests. The json string provided by buildQuery(Predicate) can be used with _search get requests of ES index to produce downloads.
